<div class="blue-background">
	<div class="row text-center big-spacer-top">
		<h1 class="animated fadeInDown">Discovery</h1>
		<p class="no-tagline animated fadeIn">Rails Engine. Personality Test.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="row big-spacer-top">
	<div class="small-12 columns">
		<p>I built this engine with the intention of plugging it into <%= link_to "major finder", "http://majorfinder.com/", class: "pink-link-center" %>.  Many people who sign up don't have any idea what they would like to do for a major or career.  This personality test is a way for them to find some ideas based on their personality.</p>

	</div>
</div>

<div class="row big-spacer-bottom">
	<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-centered columns" id="built-using">
		<ul>
			<li>Built Using</li>
			<li>Ruby & Ruby on Rails</li>
			<li>HTML</li>
			<li>Heroku</li>
			<li>Postgresql</li>
			<li>Minimal Design [IN PROCESS]</li>
			<li>CSS / SASS / Javascript / Angular JS [IN PROCESS]</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
	<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-centered columns big-spacer-bottom">
		<%= link_to "Visit Discovery on Github", "https://github.com/flores8/discovery", class: "button expand", id: "ghost-button" %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="background-gray big-spacer-top" id="work-show">
	<div class="row">
		<h4 class="text-center">See Some of My Other Projects</h4>
	</div>

	<!-- Major Finder and Discovery -->
	<div class="row big-spacer-bottom">
		<div class="small-spacer-top ">
			<div class="small-12 medium-6 columns portfolio">
				<%= link_to image_tag('work/majorfinder.jpg'), work_majorfinder_path, class: "border" %>
				<h3><%= link_to "Major Finder", work_majorfinder_path %></h3>
			</div>
			<div class="small-12 medium-6 columns portfolio">
				<%= link_to image_tag('work/bloccit.jpg'), work_bloccit_path, class: "border" %>
				<h3><%= link_to "Training Community", work_bloccit_path %></h3>
			</div>
		</div>
